  "text": "Finally, OPE is related to work on order-preserving compression [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Although some OPE schemes use similar techniques, the requirements for OPE are different: compression is not a requirement for OPE, whereas security (plaintext privacy) is not a requirement for compression.",
